'''Luhwa''' is a city in northwest [[Burundi]]. It is located close to the borders of both the [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]] and [[Rwanda]].

==References==
Fitzpatrick, M., Parkinson, T., & Ray, N. (2006) ''East Africa.'' Footscray, VIC: Lonely Planet.

